data.title: All 94 The King of Fighters Characters - Full Roster (1994-2024)
data.meta_description: The King of Fighters may not be one of the longest standing fighting game franchises, but it definitely offers the biggest character roster we've ever seen!
data.text:
The King of Fighters boasts by far the biggest character roster out of any fighting game (even from Smash Bros  which is not a fighting game?), but that also comes with a few downfalls, like having amazing new characters show up only for a couple of games, and then vanish!

This list aims to help you discover all KOF characters, and the games each one has appeared on. Feel free to browse specific KOF game rosters below:
